title: Did the CEO of the Energy Company destroy Native Americans as "dirty natives"?
subtitle: An online photo claims that the executive director of the Energy Transport Company (Kelsi Warren) made an evil comic statement on "The Dirty Native Citizens" and the demonstrators (Dakota Pipeline).
author: Kim LaCapria
vclaim: The CEO of the Energy Transport Partners (Kelsey Warren) said that the American Freedom would not be disrupted by the "dirty citizens" involved in the D.B. demonstration.
